@startuml
title Activity Diagram: findcom

start

:User executes `findcom`;

if (Input is empty?) then (yes)
    :Show invalid command format error;
    stop
else (no)
endif

:Split input by `;`;
:Trim and remove empty keywords;
:Create company keyword predicate;
:Filter displayed contact list;

